OOC: Yan, does Galaxor's sword do some special stuff?

::Abominus::
Abominus spins somewhat, deflecting Galaxor's sword on his arm 
plates, and fires a sonic concussion blast towards Galaxor as he 
falls. "Grrrrrrrrrrr"


On 15 Apr 2001, at 0:13, Yanshosh@... wrote:

> ::Galaxor::
> 
> Galaxor is hit by the punch, stumbling back. He sees Abominus being
> hit by the missile and thrown forward. Sidestepping, Galaxor puts a
> hand on Abominus's back, pushing him away and then spinning around and
> swinging his sword at him.
